{"tid":868464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【時代力量】小泳褲大秀好身材，鮮肉候選人讓網友想遷戶籍","createTime":"2018-10-19T13:16:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-19T14:10:17.000Z","uid":35221,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1f17005333cdd48349652e6c55cc92cac6b16d72","tid":868464,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T13:16:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpVf3ULa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpVf3ULa.jpg&h=1b469b2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唐聖捷引爆網路話題，他在競選文宣上僅穿泳褲，露出結實好身材，令網友直呼「小鮮肉很可以」。（圖擷取自時代力量）<br />\n<br />\n2018-10-19 20:21<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕11月24日九合一大選今（19）日進行候選人號次抽籤，新北市議員時代力量候選人唐聖捷引爆網路話題，他在競選文宣上僅穿泳褲，露出結實好身材，令網友直呼「小鮮肉很可以」、「現在遷戶籍也來不及了」。<br />\n<br />\n時代力量新北市新莊、五股、泰山、林口議員13號候選人唐聖捷，可見他在拍攝競選文宣定裝照時，只穿著水藍色泳褲，脖子上掛著黑色泳鏡，在鏡頭前方面部微微朝右露出一抹淡淡微笑，軀幹的結實好身材一覽無疑，畫面被轉貼至臉書社團「爆廢公社」引發熱議。<br />\n<br />\n文宣中旁邊的文字用倚老賣老的口吻說教：「年輕人要再勤跑一點！」，下一句拿唐聖傑的專長幽默「打臉」：「我其實用游得比較快！」這照片貼在時代力量新北市議員候選人曾柏瑜臉書上，她表示，該照片為一系列「時力新北版的打臉幹話」的其中1張，還有黃國昌與其他候選人版本的照片。<br />\n<br />\n許多網友看到這照片都對具備泳將背景的唐聖捷印象深刻，也不斷有女網友留言指稱「被政治耽誤的游泳選手」、「我要去時代力量應徵助理」、「新北的選情有這麼精彩」、「我覺得這樣很好啊」、「年輕的比較敢做事和改革」、「可惡我住彰化」、「他本人蠻帥的我看過還握過手」。<br />\n<br />\n唐聖捷宣布參選時曾說，自己是第1位宣布參選運動選手理事的選手，過程充滿黑箱，最後雖吊車尾當選泳協理事，也體認到體育改革不只是參與泳協改選，希望從地方政治出發，讓體育變得更好。<br />\n<br />\n轉自自由時報網站<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2586108\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2586108&d=hnmXpn6FTcVCC8%2BBwQ8XxTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=5f0fc450\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2586108&h=33fbe969\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2586108</a><br />\n<br />\n唐聖捷Facebook<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/bebravechieh/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbebravechieh%2F&d=hnmXpn6FTcVCC8%2BBwQ8XxTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=7a739dfe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/bebravechieh/</a>"},{"pid":"46b8d7663d868d1c0bc7c41b48350855fac84ba8","tid":868464,"uid":35221,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T13:17:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/44319291_1365721270224858_2998243478799908864_n.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;oh=275ed1cf0858bd0bf609fe3ff928d040&amp;oe=5C501E90\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F44319291_1365721270224858_2998243478799908864_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26oh%3D275ed1cf0858bd0bf609fe3ff928d040%26oe%3D5C501E90&h=a95e39f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/44269402_1365721736891478_5458236837111791616_n.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;oh=ea1349e1d00ecea52839196a543925fd&amp;oe=5C4DF8E5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F44269402_1365721736891478_5458236837111791616_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26oh%3Dea1349e1d00ecea52839196a543925fd%26oe%3D5C4DF8E5&h=80940923&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/44245541_1365721376891514_3578025018212220928_n.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;oh=4948f27a1a2e33b51e7fe7872118a408&amp;oe=5C4F9682\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F44245541_1365721376891514_3578025018212220928_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D104%26oh%3D4948f27a1a2e33b51e7fe7872118a408%26oe%3D5C4F9682&h=99094eb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/44237362_1365721576891494_6644328034843230208_n.jpg?_nc_cat=103&amp;oh=f02de30c5215dd05f76b3ea6bbc5e910&amp;oe=5C52F01A\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F44237362_1365721576891494_6644328034843230208_n.